Composition (HAS-A Relationship)

This is one of the most important concepts used in your program.

What is Composition?

Composition means one class contains another class as a member.

Example:

private Exam exam;

Inside Student class.

This means:

Student HAS-A Exam

So a student contains exam marks.

Diagram
Student
   |
   | HAS-A
   |
Exam
In your constructor
public Student(int age, String name, int id, String gender, String email, Exam exam)

You pass the Exam object inside the Student.

Example:

